          Same engine. Three isolation surfaces.
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-[15px] text-foreground/70 leading-relaxed">
          Free pool mailboxes never silently appear in the premium pool. Recovery pool is for paid mailboxes serving a cooldown. Dedicated infrastructure is isolation at the worker layer, not a reputation shortcut.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-[14px] bg-white ring-1 ring-[color:var(--border)] overflow-hidden">
        <!-- Row: Free pool -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-[160px_1fr_auto] gap-6 px-7 py-6 items-center border-b border-[color:var(--border)]">
